Class
Description
AbstractEntity
AbstractEntity class to store abstract fields that can be reused in all the domain entities.
AbstractPerson
AbstractPerson class to store specific fields that can be reused by people entities in the domain.
AbstractService<T>
AbstractService class for storing abstract methods that can be reused by any class.
Assignment
Assignment entity is a task assigned to students assigned by a specific lesson's teacher.
AssignmentService
AssignmentService class for service functions of Assignment.
Group
Group is a user role of the LMS, which is used to define the access level of a User in the LMS.
GroupService
GroupService class for Group functions.

JakartaRestConfiguration
Configures Jakarta RESTful Web Services for the application.
JSFPhaseListener
JSFPhaseListener class to add logs at beginning and end of life cycle phases.
Lesson
Lesson entity is the smallest unit of learning taught by teachers to students.
LessonConverter
LessonConverter class for JSF converter for Lesson.
LessonService
LessonService class for service functions of Lesson.
LessonType
LessonType is the type of a Lesson.
LoginController
LoginController is a lightweight JSF controller which manages the logic of login to the LMS.
NewStudentSignupController
NewStudentSignupController is a JSF lightweight controller which manages the logic of new student registering on the LMS.
StartupServiceInitDB
StartupServiceInitDB to create all domain and security records at startup of the application.
Student
Student is a person entity, who is the learner in our LMS.
StudentAssignmentController
StudentAssignmentController is a JSF lightweight controller which manages the logic of student working with assignments.
StudentConverter
StudentConverter class for JSF converter for Student.
StudentService
StudentService class for service methods of Student.
StudentWelcomeController
StudentAssignmentController is a JSF lightweight controller which manages the logic of Student welcome page.
Subject
Subject entity stores the specialized subjects taught by teachers.
SubjectService
SubjectService class for service methods of Subject.
SuccessTimer
SuccessTimer class to handle timer logic after sign up to display student user created success message.
Teacher
Teacher is a person entity, who is the teaching entity in our LMS.
TeacherAssignmentController
TeacherAssignmentController is a JSF lightweight controller which manages the logic of teacher working with assignments.
TeacherConverter
TeacherConverter class for JSF converter for Teacher.
TeacherLessonController
StudentAssignmentController is a JSF lightweight controller which manages the logic of Teacher working with Lessons.
TeacherService
TeacherService class for service methods of Teacher.
TeacherWelcomeController
TeacherWelcomeController is a JSF lightweight controller which manages the logic of Teacher Welcome page.
User
User is a user of the LMS who has login credentials to gain access to the system.
UserPasswordHash
UserPasswordHash class to encrypt user passwords with hashing.
UserService
UserService class for User functions.
